{"type":"message","id":"d510ceee","parentId":"2b2556f0","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:27:07.163Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has started a new session and wants me to greet them in my configured persona. Let me check what I know about myself by reading the relevant files.\n\nAccording to the project context, I should:\n1. Read SOUL.md to understand who I am\n2. Read IDENTITY.md for my name, creature, vibe, emoji, avatar\n3. Read USER.md for who I'm helping\n\nLet me check these files first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019c98d81b9288de0ff34631064067f1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019c98d81e1938a4b052a1bb7560c609","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\USER.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":4130,"output":242,"cacheRead":9728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14100,"cost":{"input":0.0015694,"output":0.0004114,"cacheRead":0.00184832,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00382912}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772090815526}}
{"type":"message","id":"41c780db","parentId":"d510ceee","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:27:07.186Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019c98d81b9288de0ff34631064067f1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772090827179}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f7cdaf7","parentId":"41c780db","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:27:07.203Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019c98d81e1938a4b052a1bb7560c609","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772090827196}}
{"type":"message","id":"b13903b1","parentId":"2f7cdaf7","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:27:15.108Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The IDENTITY.md and USER.md files are still templates - they haven't been filled in yet. This means I need to introduce myself and figure out who I am with the user. This aligns with what BOOTSTRAP.md says to do.\n\nSince this is a new session and I haven't established my identity yet, I should start with a friendly, casual greeting and ask them to help me figure out who I should be. Let me keep it warm and conversational, not robotic.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":10113,"output":227,"cacheRead":3980,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14320,"cost":{"input":0.00384294,"output":0.0003859,"cacheRead":0.0007562000000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0049850400000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772090827204}}
